channel.title: Peace
channel.description:
[size=15pt]dont know why i posted this in server discussion, dont care[/size] I suppose I'm gonna follow up on tyb and leave mopar, goodbye. Buttt before I go, I wanna write a little bit more. First; I'm not leaving mopar specifically, I'm gonna try to devote more of my time to working out/getting out more. Second; I may come back from time to time to laugh at some of your server downloads (none of the ones I respect like ZH or DZ, mostly PI). Third; a little below will show a few people I respect, if you're not on the list it doesn't mean I don't love you I just forgot and didn't wanna remember I'm too tired. Time to try to clean up this clusterfuck I call a life.
LIST:
drub rand arham tyb si force<3 soul<3 bowser (we never really talked but you seemed cool) l&p (call me baby) krack ofc frell fat cookies (where the love did you go) ruby (you were an ass but always made me laugh for some reason, your a cool guy.) fails (i still got you on msn bub :P) dominic<3
Oh yeah, if you want my skype/msn (skype; ask arham 4 | msn; ask fails) Cya guys, and if I left you out and you know I like you don't take it personal I'm seriously tired.
